import imaplib
import email
import os

mail = imaplib.IMAP4_SSL('imap.gmail.com')
DownloadAdress = 'C:/Users/Patrik/Desktop/'
mail.login('kolarpatrik662', 'rikisek2003')
mail.select('INBOX')  # vybrat sloÅ¾ku

type, data = mail.search(None, 'ALL')  # vsechny ID emailu ulozi do listu
mail_ids = data[0]
id_list = mail_ids.split()

for num in data[0].split():  # rozdeli data na jednotlivy stringy(nazvy)
    typ, data = mail.fetch(num, '(RFC822)')
    raw_email = data[0][1]

    raw_email_string = raw_email.decode('utf-8')  # dekoduje mail do normalniho jazyka
    email_message = email.message_from_string(raw_email_string)

    for part in email_message.walk():  # stahne prilohu
        if part.get_content_type() == "text/plain":
            body = part.get_payload(decode=True)
            save_string = str(DownloadAdress + 'TEXT' + ".txt")

            myfile = open(save_string, 'a')
            myfile.write(body.decode('utf-8'))

            myfile.close()
        else:
            continue
        if part.get_content_maintype() == 'multipart':  # ma soubor prilohu
            continue
        if part.get('Content-Disposition') is None:  # neni prazdna
            continue
        fileName = part.get_filename()  # nacte jmeno prilohy
        if bool(fileName):
            filePath = os.path.join(DownloadAdress, fileName)  # cesta pro stazeni
            if not os.path.isfile(filePath):
                fp = open(filePath, 'wb')  # otevre soubor s nazvem prilohy
                fp.write(part.get_payload(decode=True))  # zapise zpravu
                fp.close()  # zavre soubor
print("Download Succesfull")
